question: Na-niat-ê kiann-lâi 'lâi-kàu kīn-sò-ê kiàⁿ-châi ūi-tio̍h sè-ûi chhèng-chiàⁿ hām chè-chōa-khó-lêng sè-ûi chhèng-chiàⁿ ê sî-kan, sī sím-mih nî tit-tio̍h siōng-koân ê sî-liòng?
Chit ê phioⁿ téng-bīn ê `weighted average partnership units outstanding`, saⁿ-nî ê lóng-chóng kóe-chiâⁿ-choē?
Tī siánn-ê nî-tsūn ê 'pîng-kin hû-kò-sòan ê sî-thó-thiu, ū siánn-ê 'ki-chho-sûn-lī hō͘ kong-khong kó͘-pâi'?
In 2000 ni mi 2002, 'weighted average number of common shares outstanding' ê kûi-chha̍h ū sím-mih piàn-tōng?
answer: Weighted average common shares outstanding ê só͘-chāi sī kî-tiong ê sî-kan kî-kan ū tîm-chhiúⁿ ê chìn-chham. I khai-sí tī 2000 nî ê 126,836, tòe 2001 nî ê 129,660, chiah koh cheng-tióng kàu 2002 nî ê 133,981.

question: Bo-ti̍t ê chu-liāu, 2002 nî ê sòaⁿ tòe 2000 nî ê sòaⁿ khah-sè ê, lia̍t chhut lâi.
answer: basic net income available for common shares
minority interest in earnings of common unitholders
diluted net income available for common shares and dilutive potential common shares
dilutive shares for stock-based compensation plans

question: Tī 2001 nî, 'sio̍k phàu-kè ê phoe-chhiú chhù-sò͘ kap chhiⁿ-tiāⁿ-hoat chhù-sò͘' ê tōa-pō͘-hūn sī tùi 'sio̍k phàu-kè ê hū-tông tan-ūi chiūⁿ-tiâⁿ' lâi ê, kiâⁿ-chūi chē-chē?
Nāi-bú net income tī 2002 nā-sī koh-iâⁿ 20% koân, hit ê sann-ê liân ê tiong-kan ná-iâⁿ basic net income ūi-tōe tú-tú tio̍h tú?
Tùi chû-liāu lâi kóng, sī ū tìn-tsí ê 'tōng-iōng-chhè ê pêng-kun sò͘-liòng chiūⁿ-tâi' hām 'chòe ki-pún ê hông-lī sī hòan-chiok tòe ê' chit nn̄g ê phóe-tāi chha-iā ū tìn-tsí ê koan-liân bô?
answer: In-lāi ū chin tìn-tsí chha-iā. 2000 chì 2002 nî, tōng-iōng-chhè ê pêng-kun sò͘-liòng tō oân-tsuátn-á tōa, tòe-tit-á tō tiāu--khì, chiâⁿ-chòe 2001 nî siōng-koân, tān-sī 2002 nî tō tiāu-kàu siōng-tâi. Hit nî ê tōng-iōng-chhè sò͘-liòng sī siōng-koân ê, tān-sī hông-lī sī siōng-chha̍t ê. Chit-ê ì-bī-tio̍h-sī, só͘-í tōng-iōng-chhè sò͘-liòng tōa, hông-lī bōe tōa-sò͘-sò͘, tān-sī siōng-koân ê chhè sò͘-liòng tòe-tit-á tō kaù-sú siōng-chha̍t ê hông-lī.

question: 予"basic"抑 "diluted" 两种收入指标，哪一种个值所有年拢较高？
answer: diluted net income available for common shares and dilutive potential common shares

question: Achiok ê chha-sòan-sòan ê siâu-tīnn, tī chha-sòan-sòan ê nî kah 2002 chi-kan, ū siáⁿ-chiáⁿ châi-lí ê hong-sèⁿ siâⁿ-chòe tō tōa-tōa ê hē-chí?
answer: diluted net income available for common shares and dilutive potential common shares

question: 2000 nî kàu 2002 nî, hō͘ ko-teng kó͘-chha̍h ū-hêng ê ki-pún net siu-ji̍p tùi chē-chē chiūⁿ kàu chē-chē ē?
